article_title: Netanyahu: 'The victory has a very heavy price'
sentence: He  adds:  "This  victory  has  a  very  heavy  price  to  pay,"  and  acknowledges  that  some  members  of  the  Israel  Defense  Forces  (IDF)  will  die  during  the  war.

article_title: Netanyahu: 'The victory has a very heavy price'
sentence: He  says  he  has  been  told  by  the  families  of  soldiers  killed  in  combat  to  continue  fighting.
